'''畸胎瘤'''（{{lang-en|Teratoma}}）源自于多能性[[原始生殖细胞|原始生殖细胞]]或[[胚胎干细胞|胚胎干细胞]]向[[胚层|胚层组织]]分化所形成的瘤；其成分包含[[细胞分化|已分化]]胚层组织和[[细胞分化|未分化]]细胞，两者杂乱聚集或结构错乱排列。大多数畸胎瘤含有二至三个胚层组织成分，偶见仅含一个胚层组织成分；肿瘤组织多数成熟，少数未成熟，且多数为囊性，少数为实性。畸胎瘤好发于卵巢、睾丸、尾骨、纵隔、腹膜后。

畸胎瘤主要分成两种类型，即「成熟型畸胎瘤」（{{lang|en|mature teratoma}}）与「未成熟畸胎瘤」（{{lang|en|immature teratoma}}）。其中成熟型畸胎瘤占95%至98%；而未成熟畸胎瘤只有2%至5%。成熟畸胎瘤通常在女性身上发现，未成熟畸胎瘤却经常发现于男性。

畸胎瘤是一种常见的[[卵巢|卵巢]]肿瘤，发病率占全部卵巢原发性肿瘤的15%，为实心或囊心、被膜包覆的[[腫瘤|腫瘤]]。在腫瘤中可以看到许多类似正常的器官组织，比如毛发、软骨与腺体等。尽管这些特殊组织看似正常，但经常与周围组织无关（比如在软骨的周围形成角质）。在过往医学报告中，毛发、牙齿、硬骨甚至是高度分化的器官如眼<ref name="pmid6540049">{{cite journal| author = Chi JG, Lee YS, Park YS, Chang KY| title = Fetus-in-fetu: report of a case| journal = American Journal of Clinical Pathology| volume = 82| issue = 1| pages = 115–9| pmid = 6540049| doi =| url =https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-clinical-pathology_1984-07_82_1/page/n136|date=July 1984}}</ref><ref name="pmid9841706">{{cite journal| author = Sergi C, Ehemann V, Beedgen B, Linderkamp O, Otto HF| title = Huge fetal sacrococcygeal teratoma with a completely formed eye and intratumoral DNA ploidy heterogeneity| journal = Pediatric and Developmental Pathology : the Official Journal of the Society for Pediatric Pathology and the Paediatric Pathology Society| volume = 2| issue = 1| pages = 50–7| year = 1999| pmid = 9841706| doi =| url =}}</ref>、手、脚、肢体<ref name="pmid14745894">{{cite journal| author = Kuno N, Kadomatsu K, Nakamura M, Miwa-Fukuchi T, Hirabayashi N, Ishizuka T| title = Mature ovarian cystic teratoma with a highly differentiated homunculus: a case report| journal = Birth Defects Research. Part a, Clinical and Molecular Teratology| volume = 70| issue = 1| pages = 40–6| pmid = 14745894| doi = 10.1002/bdra.10133| url =|date=January 2004}}</ref><ref name="pmid19184054">{{cite journal| author = Arlikar JD, Mane SB, Dhende NP, Sanghavi Y, Valand AG, Butale PR| title = Fetus in fetu: two case reports and review of literature| journal = Pediatric Surgery International| volume = 25| issue = 3| pages = 289–92| pmid = 19184054| doi = 10.1007/s00383-009-2328-8| url =|date=March 2009}}</ref>等，都曾在畸胎瘤中发现，但形成完整器官的比率不高<ref>{{cite news | title = Tumor in baby’s brain contained tiny foot | publisher = msnbc.msn.com | date = December 18, 2008 | url = http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/28294470/ | accessdate = 2008-12-19 | archive-date = 2008-12-19 | archive-url = https